%a{ name: 'data_retention'}
%h2 Data retention
%ul
  %li Upon deleting your account all your data is deleted from the database.
  %li Upon deleting any of your data (e.g. an email reminder) it is purged from the database after 3 months, this allows for recovery in the event of accidental deletion.
  %li Your data from OSM is retained in a cache on the server for upto 10 minutes.
  %li Web server logs are retained on the server for upto 1 month.
  %li Backups of the servers (which include the database and logs) are retained for upto six months.
  %li Statistics that you contribute to (such as total user accounts on a date or total number of website visitors during a given hour) are retained indefinatly.


